@startuml
[*] --> GENERATED : Customer requests token

GENERATED --> WAITING : Token placed in queue
WAITING --> CALLED : Operator calls token
WAITING --> SKIPPED : No response

CALLED --> IN_SERVICE : Customer arrives
CALLED --> SKIPPED : Customer absent

IN_SERVICE --> COMPLETED : Service delivered

COMPLETED --> [*]
SKIPPED --> [*]

note right of WAITING
  Priority score
  determines position
end note

note right of IN_SERVICE
  Timer tracks
  service duration
end note
@enduml